title: Citzens Co-op
description: Locally operated and owned natural food store. Stocks organic vegetable, dried goods, bulk food, and household products. Makes an effort to sell products made locally i.e. fresh bread from local bakery, coffee from local roasters. Not all veg but does labeled vegan things and has a vegan refrigerator section with vegan mayo, vegan cheese, and non-dairy yogurt. Usually hosts a small farmers market on Sunday at 2pm. Parking is in dirt lot surrounded by chain link fence on adjacent street.
